fields.description.content: [{'type': 'paragraph', 'content': [{'type': 'text', 'text': 'User Story:'}]}, {'type': 'paragraph', 'content': [{'type': 'text', 'text': 'As a developer, when I use the intersection observer hook, I expect to be able to remove the observer after it fires.'}]}, {'type': 'paragraph', 'content': [{'type': 'text', 'text': 'How it works In Floating CTA', 'marks': [{'type': 'strong'}]}, {'type': 'text', 'text': ':  the icons load in and load out using the intersection component when not in view. We still want this functionality. '}]}, {'type': 'paragraph', 'content': [{'type': 'text', 'text': 'How it works in Browse Cards Page: ', 'marks': [{'type': 'strong'}]}, {'type': 'text', 'text': 'Image loads in when in view and then intersection observer is removed as to not trigger another re-render.'}]}, {'type': 'paragraph', 'content': [{'type': 'text', 'text': 'We want both implementations to exist but need a way to toggle the behavior. '}]}, {'type': 'paragraph', 'content': [{'type': 'text', 'text': 'Reference:', 'marks': [{'type': 'strong'}]}]}, {'type': 'paragraph', 'content': [{'type': 'inlineCard', 'attrs': {'url': 'https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/API/IntersectionObserver/unobserve'}}, {'type': 'text', 'text': ' '}]}]

fields.description.content: [{'type': 'paragraph', 'content': [{'type': 'text', 'text': 'This spike results from '}, {'type': 'inlineCard', 'attrs': {'url': 'https://creditonebank.atlassian.net/browse/DPM-7875'}}, {'type': 'text', 'text': ' '}]}, {'type': 'bulletList', 'content': [{'type': 'listItem', 'content': [{'type': 'paragraph', 'content': [{'type': 'text', 'text': 'While testing the OTP flow for PQ and PQ of One, QA observed on TEST03 that when applicants get directed from the ‘Verification’ Page to the ‘Passcode Send’ page, they see a spinner on the Verification Page, but after being directed to the ‘Passcode Send’ Page, if there is a delay in page load, the ‘Passcode Send’ page appears blank. Therefore the user has no information on whether they should stay on the page and wait for it to load. This is because on a slow network, it takes a while for the resources to be dowloaded for that page. '}]}]}, {'type': 'listItem', 'content': [{'type': 'paragraph', 'content': [{'type': 'text', 'text': 'As part of the above ticket,'}, {'type': 'mention', 'attrs': {'id': '712020:238b19cc-0680-486b-80b3-e2566d1c6c20', 'text': '@Tariq Shams', 'accessLevel': '', 'localId': 'df6d1b49-a746-4403-bb3f-ed6b6d1a6cf4'}}, {'type': 'text', 'text': ' & '}, {'type': 'mention', 'attrs': {'id': '5d4aec6c0fa6d40d14fc7655', 'text': '@Eric Feuerstein', 'accessLevel': '', 'localId': 'fa262cd5-a0bf-47fd-8586-dc29c99395cb'}}, {'type': 'text', 'text': 'determined that it might be possible to have some logic in the page template that could display a spinner in the event that all the other resources have to be downloaded. This wouldn’t completely solve having a blank page displayed at all, but it could reduce the amount of time that it takes to show something to the user, so they are prompted to remain on that page. '}]}]}]}, {'type': 'paragraph', 'content': [{'type': 'text', 'text': 'Therefore, please investigate further the most feasible solution to displaying a spinner on the ‘Passcode Send’ page, so the applicants don’t just see a blank page and are informed to wait, while the resources are being loaded on that page. Please also determine if the spinner can be implemented on each page of the Acquisitions flow.'}]}, {'type': 'panel', 'content': [{'type': 'paragraph', 'content': [{'type': 'text', 'text': 'This ticket requires QC only if only the solution is proposed. fields.description.content: [{'type': 'paragraph', 'content': [{'type': 'text', 'text': 'We would like to update the Missing Information Status on the Application Status page so that instead of form fields, the user is shown a static text response in a gray box (like for Application Approved), that is authorable (with the capability created in'}, {'type': 'inlineCard', 'attrs': {'url': 'https://creditonebank.atlassian.net/browse/DPM-7874'}}, {'type': 'text', 'text': ').'}]}, {'type': 'paragraph', 'content': []}, {'type': 'mediaSingle', 'attrs': {'layout': 'align-start'}, 'content': [{'type': 'media', 'attrs': {'type': 'file', 'id': 'b6ae9915-e32f-42d0-9ef6-0a5414dda360', 'alt': 'image-20240916-231236.png', 'collection': '', 'height': 691, 'width': 1320}}]}, {'type': 'paragraph', 'content': [{'type': 'text', 'text': 'USER STORY', 'marks': [{'type': 'strong'}]}]}, {'type': 'paragraph', 'content': [{'type': 'text', 'text': 'As an applicant whose multi-account application is missing information, when I check my application status, I expect to see a message letting me know to expect a letter in the mail so that I understand what the next steps to process my application are.'}]}, {'type': 'paragraph', 'content': []}, {'type': 'panel', 'content': [{'type': 'paragraph', 'content': [{'type': 'text', 'text': 'This ticket requires QC and QA'}]}], 'attrs': {'panelType': 'warning'}}, {'type': 'panel', 'content': [{'type': 'paragraph', 'content': [{'type': 'text', 'text': 'We might not use this API anymore once this ticket completes'}]}], 'attrs': {'panelType': 'info'}}, {'type': 'paragraph', 'content': [{'type': 'text', 'text': 'Compliance approval attached'}]}, {'type': 'mediaGroup', 'content': [{'type': 'media', 'attrs': {'type': 'file', 'id': 'e24a64b5-1b67-49fa-8994-e5eccde52595', 'collection': ''}}]}, {'type': 'paragraph', 'content': []}]
